"Give It 2 U" is a song by American R&B recording artist Robin Thicke, featuring vocals from American rapper Kendrick Lamar. The song was initially released on July 2, 2013 as a promo single before officially being serviced to US Top 40/Mainstream radio on August 27, 2013 as the third single from Thicke's sixth studio album, Blurred Lines (2013). The song, produced by Dr. Luke and Cirkut, was written by the two alongside William Adams, Robin Thicke and Kendrick Lamar Duckworth. It has so far peaked at number 43 on the ARIA chart in Australia.
